<span id="freeTextContainer17562434703793574177">This was a very touching story of a teenager being bullied, (to me it seems like it was a documentary told in a story form). The story has great details. I was able to feel what Kevin was feeling and side with him. I may not agree with what he did, but I understand.</span>

