<span id="freeTextContainer4089671987510438043">This book is very good except for being very in-depth in spots. I am not a detail kind of reader. When I started this the pages just reached out and grabbed me, I couldn&apos;t put it down! About a third of the way through, it started to get technical and to me a little boring. I understood these details had to be in there to understand what was going on so I plowed through and it was well worth it. It opened my eyes to things I didn&apos;t know before and made me think. I recommend Betrayal High to every</span>
  <span id="freeText4089671987510438043" style="display:none">This book is very good except for being very in-depth in spots. I am not a detail kind of reader. When I started this the pages just reached out and grabbed me, I couldn't put it down! About a third of the way through, it started to get technical and to me a little boring. I understood these details had to be in there to understand what was going on so I plowed through and it was well worth it. It opened my eyes to things I didn't know before and made me think. I recommend Betrayal High to everyone. It is THAT good!</span>
