        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer3664370078" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer5502061756888587429">What a story!!!!!! This book draws you in, it keeps you there and makes it hard to put down! THe author wrote this book so well that you feel as if you are there, as if you are watching every little thing that happens, every little thing that is said! This is a hard book that touches on a topic that we have faced in this world. Job well done writing this book! </span>

          </span>
