              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer3677271707650004898">I couldn&apos;t get through this. This book is politically driven and uses a high school shooting to enforce gun control. The focus is money and politics, not emotion or compassion.<br/><br/>I also struggled to get into the writing style and couldn&apos;t jive with the main family at all. I really couldn&apos;t stand them and couldn&apos;t find them believable. <br/><br/>This wasn&apos;t for me.<br/><br/>*Free electronic copy received in exchange for an honest review</span>
