  <span id="freeText12687453486608508003" style="display:none">Betrayal High is book 5 in the Zach Blake series and, like the previous 4 books, I gave it 5 stars!<br /><br />Each book in the series has had a main topic of discussion, for this book, it's bullying. This is such an important topic to discuss. I enjoy reading fictional stories that aren't afraid to broach real life subject matter and Mark M. Bello does this very well. His detailed writing carries the story forward and his characters bring it to life. <br />I recommend this series to anyone who enjoys books with suspense, drama, action, well-written characters, and interesting plots. A must read series!</span>
