<a href="https://www.goodreads.com/book/show/41591675-betrayal-in-blue"><img alt="Betrayal In Blue (A Zachary Blake Betrayal Series Book 3)" style="height: 75px;" src="https://i.gr-assets.com/images/S/compressed.photo.goodreads.com/books/1535858502l/41591675._SY75_.jpg" />
